=== Analysis Plan

    - Primary analysis: Linear mixed-effects model comparing serum IL-6 trajectory over 12 months between arms
    - Secondary outcomes: ANCOVA for Bell scale and other clinical outcomes at 12 months, adjusted for baseline values
    - Mediation analysis: Does change in sleep quality mediate the relationship between treatment arm and inflammation?
    - Adherence analysis: Among immediate arm, does CPAP adherence predict inflammatory marker improvements?


